Package com.complexible.common.openrdf.util

Provides convenience classes for OpenRDF (Sesame) library.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdunaIterations
    Utility methods for Aduna Iterations not already present in Iterations
    Expression
    Class to represent an OWL Axiom (or Axioms) as a collection of RDF statements.
    ExpressionFactory
    Factory for creating Expressions which are collections of RDF statements that are equivalent to the OWL axiom(s) they represent as defined by the OWL2 to RDF mapping spec.
    ExpressionFactory.ClassExpression
    An expression about a class
    ExpressionFactory.Datatype
    A datatype expression
    ExpressionFactory.Datatypes
    Class which represents the various different datatypes
    ExpressionFactory.ExpressionList<T extends Expression>
    Expression which represents an rdf:List of other expressions.
    ExpressionFactory.FacetRestriction
    A restriction on a facet of a datatype.
    ExpressionFactory.NamedDatatype
    A named datatype expression
    ExpressionFactory.PropertyExpression
    An expression about a property
    ExpressionFactory.RestrictedDatatype
    A user-defined datatype which has facet restrictions placed on its value
    KBModel
    An implementation of a Graph which acts as a VERY minimal OWL knowledge base.
    ModelBuilder
    Utility class for creating a set of statements using ResourceBuilders.
    ModelBuildingRDFHandler
    Implementation of an RDFHandler which collects statements from the handler events and puts them into a Graph object.
    OWL2
    Vocabulary for OWL2
    RDFByteSource
    A ByteSource whose contents is RDF serialized in some format.
    ResourceBuilder
    Utility class for creating statements about a particular resource.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ExpressionFactory.Facet
    Enumeration of the possible facets for a ExpressionFactory.FacetRestriction on a ExpressionFactory.NamedDatatype
